  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this project is to compare two pharmacist-led population management strategies
      designed to increase the rate of appropriate monitoring of vitamin B12 and serum creatinine
      for patients taking metformin.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
